<li><a href="/wiki/Elmer_Bernstein" title="Elmer Bernstein">Elmer Bernstein</a>, composer and conductor<sup id="cite_ref-47" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-47" title=""><span>[</span>48<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
